short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to generate fake data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Fake Data Generator is a powerful Chrome extension designed to generate fake data for developers, testers, and data analysts. With just one click, you can quickly create names, addresses, social id for any language/country, emails, phone numbers, and other types of dummy data to test applications, systems, or protect sensitive information during presentations and demos.
